android_install_step_one:
1. Vula isikhangeli sefowuni yakho
  2. Cofa apha  bit.ly/concompass
  3. Yongeza iCompass yoMgaqo-siseko kwiscreen sasekhaya ibhena kwaye ulandele imiyalelo
android_install_step_two:
Ukuba ibhena ayibonakali, cofa kwibar yeSixhobo kwi

kwikona ephezulu ngasekunene, emva koko ucofe "Faka i-App".
android_install_step_three: Ukuvula i-App, yifumane kwiscreen sakho sasekhaya
cases_feature_text: Khawuleza ukhangele kuhlelo oludityanisiweyo noluhlaziyiweyo lweMithetho yeNdlu yoWiso-mthetho.
guides_feature_text: Izikhokelo ezikhawulezayo kwinjongo nentsingiselo yecandelo ngalinye loMqulu wamaLungelo kunye nezinye izahluko ezisetyenziswa kakhulu zoMgaqo-siseko.
if_no_safari_instruction:
• Vula isiphequluli sakho seSafari
    Qaphela: Kufuneka kube yiSafari, awukwazi ukusebenzisa uGoogle Chrome okanye Firefox.
  • Cofa apha  bit.ly/concompass
ios_install_text:
• Skrolela ezantsi kwaye ucofe "Yongeza kwiSkrini saseKhaya" emva koko ucofe "Yongeza"
  • Ukuvula i-App, yifumane kwiscreen sakho sasekhaya
main_content:
Ikhampasi yoMgaqo-siseko

I-App yoMgaqo-siseko yaMalungu ePalamente.

Brawusa, khangela kwaye uqonde uMgaqo-siseko waseMzantsi Afrika kunye nendlela esebenza ngayo kumntu wonke. Ihlaziywa rhoqo kwaye igcinwe Umgaqo-siseko kunye  Imigaqo yeNdlu yoWiso-mthetho yeSizwe .
rules_feature_text: Izikhokelo ezifikelelekayo kwiNkundla yoMgaqo-siseko yoMzantsi Afrika ekutolikweni okugunyazisiweyo koMgaqo-siseko.
search_feature_text: Phendla kuMgaqo-siseko, iMithetho, iziKhokelo okanye aMatyala ukufumana ulwazi oludingayo.
tap_share_icon_text: Cofa i icon yokwabelana ezantsi kwesikrini
